{"tid":1425794,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家唔好再幫襯金拱門啦","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:01:31.000Z","uid":254809,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d84167ff9e0b2b3849d5cec0c3ddf4ba365902bb","tid":1425794,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:59:13.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac用<br />\n我fd係一個男人都忍唔住喊<br />\n講話5號晚點解唔比啲crew走 有咩事邊個負責<br />\n我唔該大家有骨氣少少 食少啲 等佢生意有影響<br />\n我3／8係尖沙咀夢遊時係m記門口聽到個餐廳經理講<br />\n如果一間掟催淚彈你都係要落閘架<br />\n個寫字樓竟然講:到時先算啦<br />\n我屌你呀金拱門 咩叫到時先算呀<br />\n唔好質疑我點解知係寫字樓 我做撚左接近七年 好撚清楚呢間係咩垃圾公司<br />\n十號風球山竹打撚到仆街都照開門 叫啲crew照返工 講話早啲出門口 我屌你 我瞓公司好唔好？<br />\n壞冷氣照開門 做到有crew暈底就借隔離鋪啲crew 唔撚講以為每個月個幾百萬生意有得分<br />\n某啲經理做到淨係識理個生意額 唔撚理自己員工安全！！！！！！<br />\n我求下香港人有啲骨氣 食其他啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jsk4BjS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjsk4BjS.jpg&h=45b2293a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Wbjqdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Wbjqdd.jpg&h=3485034c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjBzd6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjBzd6z.jpg&h=dc6a222e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRDawTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRDawTf.jpg&h=a1552cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cR9Eqdg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcR9Eqdg.jpg&h=2061b284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPaDFMw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPaDFMw.jpg&h=87ec1736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A65DFMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA65DFMv.jpg&h=12c9b074&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86d865b1ce53faff402064c8dcb1a88ab8cd90dd","tid":1425794,"uid":254809,"like":0,"di